    "body": "After checking the implementation, we use [`Array.prototype.find`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/find), which is not supported by IE by default.\r\n\r\nFor the widget to work in IE, you can add polyfills to your page:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<script src=\"https://polyfill.io/v3/polyfill.min.js?features=default,Array.prototype.find,Array.prototype.includes\"></script>\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe'll make sure to document that on the new documentation website.",
